<title>Volume vs. Temperature of a Gas</title>
<media id="idp349424" alt=""><image src="../../media/fig3-1914.png" mime-type="image/png"/><image for="pdf" src="../../media/fig3-643e.eps" mime-type="application/postscript"/></media>
